productComments.commentText:
Welcome to the 2024 APAC Championship Weekend on the beautiful Gold Coast!

Experienced Spartan racers have long loved the previous races held at this location in QLD, thanks to the diversity Spartan are able to create with the courses.

Spartans will be challenged with hill climbs and elevation, trawl through meandering creeks, across open paddocks, technical rocky terrain, and some great sections through the forest like settings.

Selamat datang di Akhir Pekan Kejuaraan APAC 2024 di Gold Coast yang indah!

Pembalap Spartan berpengalaman telah lama menyukai balapan sebelumnya yang diadakan di lokasi ini di QLD, berkat keberagaman yang mampu diciptakan Spartan dengan lintasannya.

Spartan akan ditantang dengan pendakian dan ketinggian bukit, menjelajahi sungai yang berkelok-kelok, melintasi padang terbuka, medan berbatu teknis, dan beberapa bagian besar melalui pengaturan seperti hutan.

Bienvenue au week-end du championnat APAC 2024 sur la magnifique Gold Coast!

Les coureurs Spartan expriments aiment depuis longtemps les courses prcdentes organises  cet endroit du QLD, grce  la diversit que Spartan est capable de crer avec les parcours.

Les Spartiates seront mis au dfi avec des montes et des lvations de collines, du chalutage dans des ruisseaux sinueux  travers des enclos ouverts, des terrains rocheux techniques et de superbes sections  travers des dcors de fort.

2024  APAC  !

 QLD

Bienvenido al fin de semana del campeonato APAC 2024 en la hermosa Gold Coast!

A los corredores experimentados de Spartan les encantan desde hace mucho tiempo las carreras anteriores celebradas en este lugar en QLD, gracias a la diversidad que Spartan puede crear con los recorridos.

Los Spartans se enfrentarn al desafo de subir colinas y elevarse, pescar a travs de arroyos serpenteantes, prados abiertos, terrenos rocosos tcnicos y algunas secciones excelentes a travs de escenarios similares a bosques.

Benvenuti al weekend del campionato APAC 2024 sulla bellissima Gold Coast!

I corridori Spartan esperti amano da tempo le gare precedenti tenutesi in questa localit nel QLD, grazie alla diversit che Spartan  in grado di creare con i percorsi.

Gli spartani saranno sfidati con salite e elevazioni in collina, con la pesca a strascico attraverso ruscelli serpeggianti, attraverso paddock aperti, terreni rocciosi tecnici e alcune fantastiche sezioni attraverso ambientazioni simili a foreste.

2024 APAC     !

           QLD        .

                     .

Willkommen zum APAC-Meisterschaftswochenende 2024 an der wunderschnen Gold Coast!

Erfahrene Spartan-Rennfahrer haben die frheren Rennen, die an diesem Ort in Queensland stattfanden, schon lange geliebt, dank der Vielfalt, die Spartan mit den Strecken schaffen kann.

Spartaner werden mit Bergaufstiegen und Hhenunterschieden, Schleppnetzen durch gewundene Bche ber offene Koppeln, technischem felsigem Gelnde und einigen tollen Abschnitten durch waldhnliche Umgebungen herausgefordert.

Bem-vindo ao fim de semana do campeonato APAC 2024 na bela Gold Coast!

Os pilotos Spartan experientes h muito adoram as corridas anteriores realizadas neste local em QLD, graas  diversidade que os Spartan so capazes de criar com os percursos.

Os espartanos sero desafiados com subidas e elevaes de colinas, arrasto atravs de riachos sinuosos, atravs de piquetes abertos, terreno rochoso tcnico e algumas grandes sees atravs da floresta como cenrios.

_source.productName: Colour Frenzy - Cairns
_source.productDescription:
Get ready for Colour Frenzya vibrant and inclusive event for everyone!

Walk, jog, run, or crawl through the 1.65km loop track with multiple colourful zones along the way. Choose 1, 2, or all 3 lapsits your call!

This is a self-paced, untimed event perfect for all ages. 80% of participants walk, making it accessible for everyone. Please note, some areas may be congested with walkers.

Experience 5 Colour Stations, a Foam Station (BUBBLES), and new inflatable crawl obstaclesits your chance to get dirty and try something new in a fun, supportive environment.

Its a day designed for making memories and enjoying the vibrant spirit of the community.

_source.productName: Perth Wildcats  v New Zealand Breakers - NBL Blitz
_source.productDescription:
Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.
_source.productShortDescription: Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament is returning.

productComments.commentText:
Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

Aps a maior e melhor Blitz da histria, a NBL tem o orgulho de anunciar que seu torneio de pr-temporada retornar  Gold Coast em setembro.

Os torcedores de todos os 10 times vero pela primeira vez as escalaes renovadas, enquanto os treinadores e jogadores ajustaro seus planos de jogo para a campanha.

O mundo do basquete chegou  Gold Coast no ano passado com mais de 40 olheiros da NBA de 27 times tendo sua primeira viso dos quatro NBL Next Stars selecionados no draft da semana passada, incluindo o nmero dois, Alex Sarr.

A Gold Coast ser novamente a sede do interesse da indstria internacional do basquete, j que o Blitz continua sendo uma viagem de reconhecimento crucial para avaliar a nova safra de times da NBL e talentos do Next Stars.

A NBL fez parceria com a Experience Gold Coast e o governo de Queensland para trazer o NBL Blitz para a Gold Coast.

Sulla scia del pi grande e migliore Blitz della storia, la NBL  orgogliosa di annunciare che il suo torneo pre-campionato torner sulla Gold Coast a settembre.

I tifosi di tutte e 10 le squadre potranno dare un primo sguardo ai roster rinnovati, mentre allenatori e giocatori metteranno a punto i loro piani di gioco per la campagna.

Il mondo del basket  arrivato alla Gold Coast lo scorso anno con pi di 40 scout NBA provenienti da 27 squadre che hanno dato il loro primo sguardo alle quattro NBL Next Stars selezionate nel draft della scorsa settimana, inclusa la scelta numero due Alex Sarr.

La Gold Coast ospiter nuovamente l'interesse dell'industria internazionale del basket, poich il Blitz rimane un viaggio di scouting cruciale per valutare il nuovo raccolto di squadre NBL e i talenti Next Stars.

La NBL ha collaborato con Experience Gold Coast e il governo del Queensland per portare l'NBL Blitz sulla Gold Coast.

la suite du plus grand et du meilleur Blitz de l'histoire, la NBL est fire d'annoncer que son tournoi de pr-saison reviendra sur la Gold Coast en septembre.

Les fans des 10 quipes auront un premier aperu des effectifs remanis, tandis que les entraneurs et les joueurs peaufineront leurs plans de match pour la campagne.

Le monde du basket-ball est venu sur la Gold Coast l'anne dernire avec plus de 40 recruteurs NBA issus de 27 quipes qui ont eu un premier aperu des quatre NBL Next Stars slectionnes lors du repchage de la semaine dernire, dont le numro deux Alex Sarr.

_source.productName: Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra | A Night At The Proms
_source.productDescription:
In a high-spirited program of music and vibrant colour, the Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) will celebrate the Last Night of The Proms with British and Australian favourites.

Featuring Australian composer Sean OBoyles Olympia Australis from the Sydney Olympics, and his Sunrise on the Coast, inspired by the Banjo Paterson poem of the same name, the concert includes The Man from Snowy River and other Australian classics from Percy Grainger, Peter Allen and The Seekers.

Soprano Renae Suttie, joined by Dean Doyle, will sing favourites from both hemispheres, such as The White Cliffs of Dover, Well Meet Again, I am Australian and I Still Call Australia Home.

With perennial British favourites including Elgars Nimrod, the Dambusters March and the Spitfire Prelude and Fugue, A Night at the Proms will be a feast of celebratory music and imagery.

Founded in 1972 and now conducted by Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, the Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra believes in providing exciting, accessible music of all periods in a relaxed and fun atmosphere.

A Night at The Proms: Celebrating the Music of Britain and Australia

In a high-spirited program of music and vibrant colour, the Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) will celebrate the Last Night of The Proms with British and Australian favourites.

Featuring Australian composer Sean OBoyles Olympia Australis from the Sydney Olympics, and his Sunrise on the Coast, inspired by the Banjo Paterson poem of the same name, the concert includes The Man from Snowy River and other Australian classics from Percy Grainger, Peter Allen and The Seekers.

Soprano Renae Suttie, joined by Dean Doyle, will sing favourites from both hemispheres, such as The White Cliffs of Dover, Well Meet Again, I am Australian and I Still Call Australia Home.

With perennial British favourites including Elgars Nimrod, the Dambusters March and the Spitfire Prelude and Fugue, A Night at the Proms will be a feast of celebratory music and imagery.

Founded in 1972 and now conducted by Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, the Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra believes in providing exciting, accessible music of all periods in a relaxed and fun atmosphere.

A Night at The Proms: Celebrating the Music of Britain and Australia

In un programma vivace di musica e colori vibranti, la Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) celebrer l'ultima notte dei balli con i favoriti britannici e australiani.

Con l'Olympia Australis del compositore australiano Sean O'Boyle delle Olimpiadi di Sydney e il suo Sunrise on the Coast, ispirato all'omonima poesia di Banjo Paterson, il concerto include The Man from Snowy River e altri classici australiani di Percy Grainger, Peter Allen e I Cercatori.

Il soprano Renae Suttie, affiancato da Dean Doyle, canter brani preferiti di entrambi gli emisferi, come The White Cliffs of Dover, We'll Meet Again, I am Australian e I Still Call Australia Home.

Con gli eterni favoriti britannici tra cui Nimrod di Elgar, Dambusters March e Spitfire Prelude and Fugue, A Night at the Proms sar una festa di musica e immagini celebrative.

Fondata nel 1972 e ora diretta dal Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, la Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra crede nella fornitura di musica emozionante e accessibile di tutti i periodi in un'atmosfera rilassata e divertente.

A Night at The Proms: Celebrare la musica della Gran Bretagna e dell'Australia

Dans un programme plein d'entrain, de musique et de couleurs vibrantes, le Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) clbrera la Last Night of The Proms avec des favoris britanniques et australiens.

Mettant en vedette Olympia Australis du compositeur australien Sean O'Boyle des Jeux olympiques de Sydney et son Sunrise on the Coast, inspir du pome de Banjo Paterson du mme nom, le concert comprend The Man from Snowy River et d'autres classiques australiens de Percy Grainger, Peter Allen. et Les Chercheurs.

La soprano Renae Suttie, accompagne de Dean Doyle, chantera des classiques des deux hmisphres, tels que The White Cliffs of Dover, We'll Meet Again, I am Australian et I Still Call Australia Home.

Avec des classiques britanniques ternels, dont Nimrod d'Elgar, la Marche des Dambusters et le Prlude et Fugue de Spitfire, A Night at the Proms sera un festin de musique et d'images de clbration.

Fond en 1972 et maintenant dirig par le Dr Fletcher Mitchell, le Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra s'engage  proposer une musique passionnante et accessible de toutes les poques dans une atmosphre dtendue et amusante.

A Night at The Proms: Clbrer la musique de Grande-Bretagne et d'Australie

En un animado programa de msica y colores vibrantes, la Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) celebrar la ltima noche de The Proms con los favoritos britnicos y australianos.

Con Olympia Australis del compositor australiano Sean O'Boyle de los Juegos Olmpicos de Sydney y su Sunrise on the Coast, inspirado en el poema Banjo Paterson del mismo nombre, el concierto incluye The Man from Snowy River y otros clsicos australianos de Percy Grainger, Peter Allen. y Los buscadores.

La soprano Renae Suttie, acompaada por Dean Doyle, cantar canciones favoritas de ambos hemisferios, como The White Cliffs of Dover, We'll Meet Again, I am Australian y I Still Call Australia Home.

Con eternos favoritos britnicos como Nimrod de Elgar, la Marcha de Dambusters y el Preludio y Fuga de Spitfire, A Night at the Proms ser una fiesta de msica e imgenes de celebracin.

Fundada en 1972 y ahora dirigida por el Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, la Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra cree en brindar msica emocionante y accesible de todas las pocas en un ambiente relajado y divertido.

Una noche en The Proms: celebrando la msica de Gran Bretaa y Australia

Num programa animado de msica e cores vibrantes, a Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) celebrar a ltima Noite dos Proms com os favoritos britnicos e australianos.

Apresentando Olympia Australis do compositor australiano Sean O'Boyle das Olimpadas de Sydney, e seu Sunrise on the Coast, inspirado no poema de Banjo Paterson de mesmo nome, o concerto inclui The Man from Snowy River e outros clssicos australianos de Percy Grainger, Peter Allen e Os buscadores.

A soprano Renae Suttie, acompanhada por Dean Doyle, cantar msicas favoritas de ambos os hemisfrios, como The White Cliffs of Dover, Well Meet Again, I am Australian e I Still Call Australia Home.

Com favoritos britnicos perenes, incluindo Nimrod de Elgar, Dambusters March e Spitfire Prelude and Fugue, A Night at the Proms ser uma festa de msica e imagens comemorativas.

Fundada em 1972 e agora dirigida pelo Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, a Orquestra Sinfnica de Sunshine Coast acredita em fornecer msica emocionante e acessvel de todos os perodos em um ambiente descontrado e divertido.

Uma noite no baile de formatura: celebrando a msica da Gr-Bretanha e da Austrlia

Dalam program musik penuh semangat dan warna-warna cerah, Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) akan merayakan Malam Terakhir The Proms bersama favorit Inggris dan Australia.

Menampilkan Olympia Australis karya komposer Australia Sean O'Boyle dari Olimpiade Sydney, dan Sunrise on the Coast-nya, yang terinspirasi oleh puisi Banjo Paterson dengan judul yang sama, konser ini menampilkan The Man from Snowy River dan karya klasik Australia lainnya dari Percy Grainger, Peter Allen dan Para Pencari.

Soprano Renae Suttie, ditemani oleh Dean Doyle, akan menyanyikan lagu-lagu favorit dari kedua belahan dunia, seperti The White Cliffs of Dover, Well Meet Again, I am Australian, dan I Still Call Australia Home.

Dengan lagu-lagu favorit Inggris selama ini termasuk Nimrod karya Elgar, Dambusters March, serta Spitfire Prelude dan Fugue, A Night at the Proms akan menjadi pesta musik dan gambar perayaan.

Didirikan pada tahun 1972 dan sekarang dipimpin oleh Dr. Fletcher Mitchell, Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra percaya dalam menyediakan musik yang menarik dan dapat diakses dari semua periode dalam suasana santai dan menyenangkan.

Mit einem stimmungsvollen Programm voller Musik und lebendiger Farben feiert das Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra (SCSO) die Last Night of The Proms mit britischen und australischen Favoriten.

Das Konzert umfasst Olympia Australis des australischen Komponisten Sean OBoyle von den Olympischen Spielen in Sydney und sein Sunrise on the Coast, das von dem gleichnamigen Gedicht von Banjo Paterson inspiriert wurde. Auerdem sind The Man from Snowy River und andere australische Klassiker von Percy Grainger, Peter Allen und The Seekers zu hren.

Die Sopranistin Renae Suttie wird zusammen mit Dean Doyle beliebte Stcke aus beiden Hemisphren singen, darunter The White Cliffs of Dover, Well Meet Again, I am Australian und I Still Call Australia Home.

Mit zeitlosen britischen Favoriten wie Elgars Nimrod, dem Dambusters March und dem Spitfire Prelude and Fugue wird A Night at the Proms ein Fest aus festlicher Musik und Bildern.

Das 1972 gegrndete und heute von Dr. Fletcher Mitchell dirigierte Sunshine Coast Symphony Orchestra legt Wert darauf, spannende, zugngliche Musik aus allen Epochen in einer entspannten und unterhaltsamen Atmosphre zu bieten.

Free camping available, with breakfast is available the next morning.

_source.productName: Big Talk One Fire First Nations Cultural Festival
_source.productDescription:
UMI Arts proudly presents the 17th annual Big Talk One Fire Cultural Festival, even bigger and better than ever in 2024! 

A day of celebration, sharing, storytelling, song, dance, art, workshops, food and yarning, all presented by First Nations performers, artists & cultural leaders from across Far North Queensland, Big Talk One Fire 2024 will again be held at at their new home at the lush Munro Martin Park in Cairns.

UMI Arts Mission is to preserve, strengthen, maintain and celebrate all aspects of Indigenous arts and culture, and Big Talk One Fire is vital to this mission. Come and join them in learning about and celebrating the strength and vibrancy of this region's First Nations people, arts and culture.

They hope you enjoy this Festival of First Nations culture!

More details to be confirmed. Watch this space!

100% fun. 100% African. 100% joy.
Cirque Africa is produced and directed by Papa Africa aka Winston Ruddle, the director who brought the hit Broadway show Cirque Mother Africa.  Cirque Africa is coming to Australia in 2024 with a brand-new show featuring the very best talent from across Africa.

Audiences will be fully immersed in traditional African culture while witnessing a handpicked world-renowned African troupe. Ranging from acrobats to dancers, musicians to contortionists masterfully performing in this energetic two-hour spectacle.

Rhythmic, colourful, energetic and awe-inspiring.

Cirque Africa artists have performed to over 2 million people worldwide and are guaranteed to captivate audiences young and old by combining the best of contortion, acrobatics, traditional dance, live music, pan spinning, hand balancing and so much more.

You wont want to miss this uniquely vibrant performance.

_source.productName: Camerata, Lou Bennett & Lior: Ngapa William Cooper (Brisbane)
_source.productDescription:
Not to be missed! Following their moving creation, Compassion, Lior and Nigel Westlake have teamed up with Lou Bennett to create Ngapa William Cooper, the extraordinarily powerful story of Yorta Yorta man, Uncle William Cooper.

Ngapa William Cooper was born out of a rich collaboration between composer Nigel Westlake, singer-songwriter Lior, and performer and academic Dr Lou Bennett AM. In this very special, completely unconducted, world premiere arrangement for chamber orchestra, Camerata and Lior once again join forces, this time with Lou Bennett, for this moving and heartfelt performance.

Ngapa William Cooper explores the strength and compassion of Yorta Yorta activist Uncle William Cooper. In 1938, Cooper led the Australian Aborigines League through the streets of Melbourne in the only non-Jewish protest worldwide against the events of Kristallnacht in Nazi Germany. Performed in English and Yorta Yorta language, it is a celebration of a man who left behind a legacy of resistance, solidarity and empathy.

In the first half, audiences will also be treated to a selection of Lior and Lous beautiful songs especially arranged for string orchestra.

Richly evocative. Artshub
Momentous. Limelight
A powerful and important work. InReview

Presented by Camerata  Queenslands Chamber Orchestra, QPAC and Brisbane Festival

Ngapa William Cooper nasceu de uma rica colaborao entre o compositor Nigel Westlake, o cantor e compositor Lior e o intrprete e acadmico Dr. Lou Bennett AM. Tidak untuk dilewatkan! Mengikuti kreasi mereka yang mengharukan, Compassion, Lior dan Nigel Westlake bekerja sama dengan Lou Bennett untuk menciptakan Ngapa William Cooper, kisah yang sangat kuat tentang pria Yorta Yorta, Paman William Cooper.

Ngapa William Cooper lahir dari kolaborasi yang kaya antara komposer Nigel Westlake, penyanyi-penulis lagu Lior, dan pemain serta akademisi Dr Lou Bennett AM. Dalam aransemen perdana dunia untuk orkestra kamar yang sangat istimewa dan sama sekali tidak dilakukan ini, Camerata dan Lior sekali lagi bekerja sama, kali ini dengan Lou Bennett, untuk pertunjukan yang mengharukan dan menyentuh hati ini.

Ngapa William Cooper mengeksplorasi kekuatan dan kasih sayang aktivis Yorta Yorta, Paman William Cooper. Pada tahun 1938, Cooper memimpin Liga Aborigin Australia melalui jalan-jalan di Melbourne dalam satu-satunya protes non-Yahudi di seluruh dunia terhadap peristiwa Kristallnacht di Nazi Jerman. Dilakukan dalam bahasa Inggris dan bahasa Yorta Yorta, ini adalah perayaan seorang pria yang meninggalkan warisan perlawanan, solidaritas dan empati.

Pada paruh pertama, penonton juga akan disuguhi pilihan lagu-lagu indah Lior dan Lou yang diaransemen khusus untuk orkestra gesek.

Kate Miller-Heidke is an award-winning singer-songwriter who traverses the worlds of folk, pop, opera and musical theatre.  She has performed on stages as varied as the Grand Ole Opry in Nashville, Coachella, the New York Metropolitan Opera, the Eurovision Song Contest, the Sydney Opera House, and the Roebuck Bay Hotel, Broome. 

And now, after long months locked away writing songs, shes hitting the road to play in dozens of beautiful theatres around Australia.

Kate will be playing her greatest hits and most beloved pop songs, as well as performing tracks from her original musicals Muriels Wedding the Musical and the new Bananaland, some unexpected covers, taking requests, and telling stories from across her varied career. Excitingly, shell also be debuting new material from her forthcoming 6th studio album, which will dive deep into the genre of gothic folk.

This is a special opportunity to see Kate in intimate, stripped-back mode, accompanied by her long-term collaborator Keir Nuttall on guitar.

Like all Kate Miller-Heidke shows, the Catching Diamonds  tour will be a celebration of voice, storytelling, emotion, humour and music that transports and transcends, of discovering anew each night the transformative connection between the performer and the audience.

Ha actuado en escenarios tan variados como el Grand Ole Opry de Nashville, Coachella, la pera Metropolitana de Nueva York, el Festival de la Cancin de Eurovisin, la pera de Sdney y el Hotel Roebuck Bay de Broome.

Y ahora, despus de largos meses encerrada escribiendo canciones, se lanza a la carretera para actuar en docenas de hermosos teatros de Australia.

Kate tocar sus grandes xitos y sus canciones pop ms queridas, adems de interpretar temas de sus musicales originales 'Muriel's Wedding the Musical' y el nuevo 'Bananaland', algunas versiones inesperadas, aceptar solicitudes y contar historias de toda su variada carrera. . Emocionantemente, tambin estrenar nuevo material de su prximo sexto lbum de estudio, que profundizar en el gnero del "folk gtico".

Dia telah tampil di berbagai panggung seperti Grand Ole Opry di Nashville, Coachella, New York Metropolitan Opera, Kontes Lagu Eurovision, Sydney Opera House, dan Roebuck Bay Hotel, Broome.

Dan sekarang, setelah berbulan-bulan terkurung dalam penulisan lagu, dia mulai tampil di puluhan teater indah di seluruh Australia.

Kate akan memainkan hits terhebatnya dan lagu-lagu pop yang paling dicintainya, serta menampilkan lagu-lagu dari musikal aslinya 'Muriel's Wedding the Musical' dan 'Bananaland' yang baru, beberapa lagu cover yang tidak terduga, menerima permintaan, dan menceritakan kisah-kisah dari berbagai kariernya. . Menariknya, dia juga akan mendebutkan materi baru dari album studio keenamnya yang akan datang, yang akan mendalami genre 'gothic folk'.

Ini adalah kesempatan istimewa untuk melihat Kate dalam mode intim dan telanjang, ditemani oleh kolaborator jangka panjangnya Keir Nuttall pada gitar.

Seperti semua pertunjukan Kate Miller-Heidke, tur Catching Diamonds akan menjadi perayaan suara, penceritaan, emosi, humor dan musik yang membawa dan melampaui, untuk menemukan hubungan transformatif antara pemain dan penonton setiap malam.

_source.productName: Simply BRILL
_source.productDescription:
Simply BRILL dramatically retells the birth of iconic songwriters such as Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil, and Ellie Greenwich. These up and coming teenage songwriters gave voice to an entire generation with hits such as Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High, and Leader of the Pack and more  all sublimely recreated with the vocal brilliance of Amelia, Michaela and Michael and a live five-piece band.

The story begins in The Brill Building  a solitary building in the heart of downtown New York City. How did one single building redefine the musical landscape and become a one stop shop hit factory in just a few short years? And how did previously unheard of teenagers steal 60's rock 'n' roll, creating a wave of hits that would be sung by all generations, right across the globe for years to come?

Theatrically presented, Simply BRILL  with its dynamic blend of history, humour and heart  takes audiences on a thrilling ride from the humble beginnings of the music business in Tin Pan Alley, through to the dawn of the singer songwriter, via the game-changing explosion of rock n roll.

productComments.commentText:
Simply BRILL dramatically retells the birth of iconic songwriters such as Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil, and Ellie Greenwich. These up and coming teenage songwriters gave voice to an entire generation with hits such as Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High, and Leader of the Pack and more  all sublimely recreated with the vocal brilliance of Amelia, Michaela and Michael and a live five-piece band.

The story begins in The Brill Building  a solitary building in the heart of downtown New York City. How did one single building redefine the musical landscape and become a one stop shop hit factory in just a few short years? And how did previously unheard of teenagers steal 60's rock 'n' roll, creating a wave of hits that would be sung by all generations, right across the globe for years to come?

Theatrically presented, Simply BRILL  with its dynamic blend of history, humour and heart  takes audiences on a thrilling ride from the humble beginnings of the music business in Tin Pan Alley, through to the dawn of the singer songwriter, via the game-changing explosion of rock n roll.

Simply BRILL racconta in modo drammatico la nascita di cantautori iconici come Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil ed Ellie Greenwich. Questi cantautori adolescenti emergenti hanno dato voce a un'intera generazione con successi come Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High e Leader of the Pack e altro ancora, il tutto ricreato in modo sublime con la brillantezza vocale di Amelia, Michaela e Michael e una band dal vivo di cinque elementi.

La storia inizia nel Brill Building, un edificio solitario nel cuore del centro di New York City. In che modo un singolo edificio ha ridefinito il panorama musicale e  diventato una fabbrica di successo in pochi anni? E come hanno fatto adolescenti inauditi a "rubare" il rock 'n' roll degli anni '60, creando un'ondata di successi che sarebbero stati cantati da tutte le generazioni, in tutto il mondo negli anni a venire?

Presentato in modo teatrale, Simply BRILL  con la sua miscela dinamica di storia, umorismo e cuore  accompagna il pubblico in un viaggio emozionante dagli umili inizi del mondo della musica a Tin Pan Alley, fino agli albori del cantautore, attraverso il gioco rivoluzionario esplosione del rock'n'roll.

Simply BRILL raconte de manire dramatique la naissance d'auteurs-compositeurs emblmatiques tels que Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil et Ellie Greenwich. Ces auteurs-compositeurs adolescents prometteurs ont donn la parole  toute une gnration avec des succs tels que Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow ?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High et Leader of le Pack et plus encore  le tout sublimement recr avec l'clat vocal d'Amelia, Michaela et Michael et un groupe live de cinq musiciens.

L'histoire commence au Brill Building, un btiment solitaire au cur du centre-ville de New York. Comment un seul btiment a-t-il redfini le paysage musical et est-il devenu en quelques annes seulement une usine  succs  guichet unique ? Et comment des adolescents jusqualors inconnus ont-ils  vol  le rocknroll des annes 60, crant une vague de tubes qui seront chants par toutes les gnrations, partout dans le monde, pendant des annes ?

Prsent en salle, Simply BRILL  avec son mlange dynamique d'histoire, d'humour et de cur  emmne le public dans un voyage passionnant depuis les humbles dbuts de l'industrie musicale  Tin Pan Alley, jusqu' l'aube de l'auteur-compositeur-interprte, en passant par le monde rvolutionnaire explosion de rock'n'roll.

Simply BRILL vuelve a contar dramticamente el nacimiento de compositores icnicos como Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil y Ellie Greenwich. Estos prometedores compositores adolescentes dieron voz a toda una generacin con xitos como Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High y Leader of the Pack y ms, todo recreado sublimemente con la brillantez vocal de Amelia, Michaela y Michael y una banda en vivo de cinco integrantes.

La historia comienza en The Brill Building, un edificio solitario en el corazn del centro de la ciudad de Nueva York. Cmo pudo un solo edificio redefinir el panorama musical y convertirse en una fbrica de xitos de ventanilla nica en tan solo unos pocos aos? Y cmo adolescentes nunca antes vistos robaron el rock 'n' roll de los 60, creando una ola de xitos que seran cantados por todas las generaciones, en todo el mundo durante los aos venideros?

Presentado teatralmente, Simply BRILL, con su combinacin dinmica de historia, humor y corazn, lleva al pblico en un viaje emocionante desde los humildes comienzos del negocio de la msica en Tin Pan Alley, hasta los albores del cantautor, pasando por la innovadora Explosin del rock'n'roll.

Simply BRILL reconta dramaticamente o nascimento de compositores icnicos como Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil e Ellie Greenwich. Esses compositores adolescentes em ascenso deram voz a uma gerao inteira com sucessos como Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High e Leader of the Pack e muito mais  tudo sublimemente recriado com o brilho vocal de Amelia, Michaela e Michael e uma banda ao vivo de cinco integrantes.

A histria comea no The Brill Building  um edifcio solitrio no corao do centro de Nova York. Como  que um nico edifcio redefiniu a paisagem musical e se tornou numa fbrica de sucessos de balco nico em apenas alguns anos? E como  que adolescentes at ento inditos roubaram o rock n roll dos anos 60, criando uma onda de xitos que seriam cantados por todas as geraes, em todo o mundo durante anos?

Apresentado teatralmente, Simply BRILL  com a sua mistura dinmica de histria, humor e emoo  leva o pblico numa viagem emocionante desde o incio humilde do mundo da msica em Tin Pan Alley, at ao nascimento do cantor e compositor, atravs da mudana de jogo exploso de rock 'n' roll.

Diese aufstrebenden Songwriter im Teenageralter gaben einer ganzen Generation mit Hits wie Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High und Leader of the Pack und mehr eine Stimme  alles wunderbar nachgebildet mit der stimmlichen Brillanz von Amelia, Michaela und Michael und einer fnfkpfigen Live-Band.

Die Geschichte beginnt im Brill Building  einem einsamen Gebude im Herzen der Innenstadt von New York City. Wie konnte ein einziges Gebude die Musiklandschaft neu definieren und in nur wenigen Jahren zu einer Hitfabrik werden, die alles aus einer Hand anbietet? Und wie konnten zuvor unbekannte Teenager den Rock 'n' Roll der 60er stahlen und eine Welle von Hits erschaffen, die noch Jahre spter von allen Generationen auf der ganzen Welt gesungen wurden?

Simply BRILL wird auf Theaterbhnen prsentiert und nimmt das Publikum mit seiner dynamischen Mischung aus Geschichte, Humor und Herz mit auf eine spannende Reise von den bescheidenen Anfngen des Musikgeschfts in Tin Pan Alley ber die bahnbrechende Explosion des Rock 'n' Roll bis hin zum Aufkommen der Singer-Songwriter.

Simply BRILL secara dramatis menceritakan kembali kelahiran penulis lagu ikonik seperti Bill Hayley & The Comets, Neil Sedaka, Bobby Darin, Carole King, Cynthia Weil, dan Ellie Greenwich. Para penulis lagu remaja yang sedang naik daun ini menyuarakan seluruh generasi dengan lagu-lagu hits seperti Rock Around The Clock, Splish Splash, Oh Carol, Will You Love Me Tomorrow?, You've Lost That Loving Feeling, River Deep Mountain High, dan Leader of the Pack dan banyak lagi  semuanya diciptakan kembali secara indah dengan kecemerlangan vokal Amelia, Michaela, dan Michael serta band live beranggotakan lima orang.

Ceritanya dimulai di The Brill Building  sebuah bangunan terpencil di jantung pusat kota New York City. Bagaimana sebuah gedung dapat mendefinisikan kembali lanskap musikal dan menjadi pabrik serba ada yang sukses hanya dalam beberapa tahun? Dan bagaimana remaja yang belum pernah terdengar sebelumnya mencuri musik rock 'n' roll tahun 60an, sehingga menciptakan gelombang lagu-lagu hits yang akan dinyanyikan oleh semua generasi, di seluruh dunia selama bertahun-tahun yang akan datang?

Disajikan secara teatrikal, Simply BRILL  dengan perpaduan dinamis antara sejarah, humor, dan hati  membawa penonton pada perjalanan yang mendebarkan dari awal mula bisnis musik yang sederhana di Tin Pan Alley, hingga awal mula penyanyi dan penulis lagu, melalui perubahan permainan. ledakan rock 'n' roll.

_source.productName: Sweet Relief! | 2024
_source.productDescription:
Sweet Relief! is here to satisfy party lovers with a nostalgia-fuelled celebration of dance floor hits, led by the icons behind them.

Taking centre stage is Kelis, the pioneer and provocateur of Y2K R&B pop, famed for her unforgettable anthem Milkshake. Making her long-awaited return to Australian shores after five years, this 2024 Australian-exclusive performance is a momentous occasion not to be missed!

Joining her are acclaimed Aussie party starters The Presets, who will perform their electrifying live show, fresh from the Eurovision stage the ever-vibrant duo Electric Fields, bold electro-pop-icons Haiku Hands, genre-bending DJ dameeeela, pop mavens JUNO and more juicy announcements to come!

Festival-goers are invited to unleash their creativity in Australia's biggest dress-up competition returning for its second sweet year and judged by our Sweet AF! star panel. The theme is "find your fit" - express yourself freely, whether you're shimmering in sequins, coordinating with your crew or serving any style that speaks to you. And of course, there's a prize waiting for the best dressed!

As always, at the beating heart of Sweet Relief! is a commitment to inclusivity and access, ensuring everyone is welcome on the dance floor. No matter who you are, get ready for a free-flowing party, destined to treat you to a moment of Sweet Relief! and leave you craving more.

Sweet Relief! is here to satisfy party lovers with a nostalgia-fuelled celebration of dance floor hits, led by the icons behind them.

Taking centre stage is Kelis, the pioneer and provocateur of Y2K R&B pop, famed for her unforgettable anthem Milkshake. Making her long-awaited return to Australian shores after five years, this 2024 Australian-exclusive performance is a momentous occasion not to be missed!

Joining her are acclaimed Aussie party starters The Presets, who will perform their electrifying live show, fresh from the Eurovision stage the ever-vibrant duo Electric Fields, bold electro-pop-icons Haiku Hands, genre-bending DJ dameeeela, pop mavens JUNO and more juicy announcements to come!

Festival-goers are invited to unleash their creativity in Australia's biggest dress-up competition returning for its second sweet year and judged by our Sweet AF! star panel. The theme is "find your fit" - express yourself freely, whether you're shimmering in sequins, coordinating with your crew or serving any style that speaks to you. And of course, there's a prize waiting for the best dressed!

As always, at the beating heart of Sweet Relief! is a commitment to inclusivity and access, ensuring everyone is welcome on the dance floor. No matter who you are, get ready for a free-flowing party, destined to treat you to a moment of Sweet Relief! and leave you craving more.

Dolce sollievo!  qui per soddisfare gli amanti delle feste con una celebrazione nostalgica dei successi della pista da ballo, guidati dalle icone dietro di loro.

Al centro della scena c' Kelis, la pioniera e provocatrice del pop R&B Y2K, famosa per il suo indimenticabile inno "Milkshake". Facendo il suo tanto atteso ritorno sulle coste australiane dopo cinque anni, questa esibizione esclusiva per l'Australia nel 2024  un'occasione importante da non perdere!

Insieme a lei ci sono gli acclamati party australiani The Presets, che si esibiranno nel loro elettrizzante spettacolo dal vivo, fresco dal palco dell'Eurovision, il sempre vibrante duo Electric Fields, le audaci icone electro-pop Haiku Hands, il DJ dameeeela che cambia genere, gli esperti del pop JUNO e altri annunci succosi in arrivo!

I partecipanti al festival sono invitati a liberare la propria creativit nella pi grande competizione di travestimenti australiana che ritorna per il suo secondo dolce anno e giudicati dalla nostra Sweet AF! pannello stellare. Il tema  "trova la tua misura": esprimiti liberamente, sia che tu stia luccicando di paillettes, coordinandoti con il tuo equipaggio o servendo qualsiasi stile che ti parli. E, naturalmente, c' un premio in attesa per il meglio vestito!

Come sempre, nel cuore pulsante di Sweet Relief!  un impegno per l'inclusivit e l'accesso, garantendo che tutti siano i benvenuti sulla pista da ballo. Non importa chi tu sia, preparati per una festa a flusso libero, destinata a regalarti un momento di dolce sollievo! e ti lasci desiderare di pi.

Festivalbesucher sind eingeladen, ihrer Kreativitt bei Australiens grtem Kostmwettbewerb freien Lauf zu lassen, der zum zweiten Mal stattfindet und von unserer Sweet AF!-Star-Jury bewertet wird. Das Motto lautet Finde deinen Platz  drcke dich frei aus, egal ob du in Pailletten schimmerst, dich mit deiner Crew abstimmst oder einen Stil trgst, der dir zusagt. Und natrlich wartet ein Preis auf die am besten gekleideten Gste!

Wie immer steht bei Sweet Relief! das Bekenntnis zu Inklusivitt und Zugang im Mittelpunkt, damit jeder auf der Tanzflche willkommen ist. Egal, wer du bist, mach dich bereit fr eine frei flieende Party, die dir einen Moment von Sweet Relief! bescheren und Lust auf mehr machen wird.

Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

_source.productName: IndigiScapes Eco Markets
_source.productDescription:
Enjoy open-air eco friendly markets in the beautiful native botanic garden surrounds at IndigiScapes!

Spend the morning wandering through the Botanic Gardens market lane and explore the range of unique stalls, sustainable products and fresh produce available from the local and creative market community.

Grab a coffee, or a bite to eat, at the IndigiCafe; or try the fantastic fare from the food vans.

Visit the popular suitcase rummage for a preloved bargain and enjoy our rummage parade on stage with Ranger Stacey.

Take a break in the shade of trees, enjoying the relaxing atmosphere with family friendly entertainment by The Little Wattlebird Band.

Children will love the flora and fauna face painting, outdoor play and nature craft where families can try random weaving and contribute weaving our garden teepee.

There is so much to see and do at the Eco Markets. Don't forget the Native Nursery will be open during the market from 8:00am to midday for all your native plant needs.

productComments.commentText:
Enjoy open-air eco friendly markets in the beautiful native botanic garden surrounds at IndigiScapes!

Spend the morning wandering through the Botanic Gardens market lane and explore the range of unique stalls, sustainable products and fresh produce available from the local and creative market community.

Grab a coffee, or a bite to eat, at the IndigiCafe; or try the fantastic fare from the food vans.

Visit the popular suitcase rummage for a preloved bargain and enjoy our rummage parade on stage with Ranger Stacey.

Take a break in the shade of trees, enjoying the relaxing atmosphere with family friendly entertainment by The Little Wattlebird Band.

Children will love the flora and fauna face painting, outdoor play and nature craft where families can try random weaving and contribute weaving our garden teepee.

There is so much to see and do at the Eco Markets. Don't forget the Native Nursery will be open during the market from 8:00am to midday for all your native plant needs.

Disfrute de mercados ecolgicos al aire libre en el hermoso jardn botnico nativo que rodea IndigiScapes!

Pase la maana paseando por la calle del mercado del Jardn Botnico y explore la variedad de puestos nicos, productos sostenibles y productos frescos disponibles en la comunidad del mercado local y creativo.

Tome un caf o coma algo en el IndigiCafe; o pruebe la fantstica comida de las furgonetas de comida.

Visite el popular almacn de maletas para disfrutar de una ganga favorita y disfrute de nuestro desfile de artculos usados en el escenario con la guardabosques Stacey.

Tmese un descanso a la sombra de los rboles y disfrute del ambiente relajante con entretenimiento familiar a cargo de The Little Wattlebird Band.

A los nios les encantar la pintura de caras de flora y fauna, los juegos al aire libre y las manualidades de la naturaleza donde las familias pueden probar a tejer al azar y contribuir a tejer nuestro tipi de jardn.

Hay mucho que ver y hacer en los Eco Markets. No olvide que el Vivero Nativo estar abierto durante el mercado desde las 8:00 am hasta el medioda para todas sus necesidades de plantas nativas.

IndigiScapes 



 IndigiCafe 

 Ranger Stacey

 8:00

Desfrute de mercados ecolgicos ao ar livre no belo jardim botnico nativo do IndigiScapes!

Passe a manh vagando pela rua do mercado do Jardim Botnico e explore a variedade de barracas exclusivas, produtos sustentveis e produtos frescos disponveis na comunidade local e criativa do mercado.

Tome um caf ou coma algo no IndigiCafe; ou experimente a comida fantstica das vans de comida.

Visite o popular local de remexer em malas para uma pechincha pr-amada e aproveite nosso desfile de remexer no palco com a Ranger Stacey.

Faa uma pausa  sombra das rvores, aproveitando a atmosfera relaxante com entretenimento familiar da The Little Wattlebird Band.

As crianas vo adorar a pintura facial da flora e da fauna, as brincadeiras ao ar livre e o artesanato natural, onde as famlias podem experimentar a tecelagem aleatria e contribuir para a tecelagem da nossa tenda de jardim.

H muito para ver e fazer nos Eco Markets. No se esquea que o Viveiro Nativo estar aberto durante o mercado das 8h00 ao meio-dia para todas as suas necessidades de plantas nativas.

Goditi i mercati ecologici all'aperto negli splendidi giardini botanici autoctoni di IndigiScapes!

Trascorri la mattinata girovagando per la corsia del mercato dei Giardini Botanici ed esplora la gamma di bancarelle uniche, prodotti sostenibili e prodotti freschi disponibili dalla comunit del mercato locale e creativo.

Prendi un caff o mangia un boccone all'IndigiCafe; oppure prova i fantastici piatti dei furgoni gastronomici.

Visita il popolare frugamento delle valigie per un affare prezioso e goditi la nostra sfilata di frugazioni sul palco con Ranger Stacey.

Prenditi una pausa all'ombra degli alberi, godendoti l'atmosfera rilassante con l'intrattenimento per famiglie della Little Wattlebird Band.

I bambini adoreranno il truccabimbi con flora e fauna, i giochi all'aperto e le attivit manuali nella natura, dove le famiglie potranno provare la tessitura casuale e contribuire a tessere il nostro teepee da giardino.

C' cos tanto da vedere e da fare agli Eco Markets. Non dimenticare che il vivaio nativo sar aperto durante il mercato dalle 8:00 a mezzogiorno per tutte le tue esigenze di piante autoctone.

Profitez des marchs cologiques en plein air dans le magnifique jardin botanique indigne d'IndigiScapes!

Passez la matine  flner dans l'alle du march des jardins botaniques et explorez la gamme de stands uniques, de produits durables et de produits frais disponibles auprs de la communaut locale et crative du march.

Prenez un caf ou une bouche  manger  l'IndigiCafe; ou essayez les plats fantastiques des camionnettes de restauration.

Visitez le populaire fouille de valises pour une bonne affaire et profitez de notre dfil de fouilles sur scne avec le Ranger Stacey.

Faites une pause  l'ombre des arbres et profitez de l'atmosphre relaxante avec les animations familiales du Little Wattlebird Band.

Les enfants adoreront le maquillage de la flore et de la faune, les jeux en plein air et l'artisanat de la nature o les familles pourront essayer le tissage alatoire et contribuer au tissage de notre tipi de jardin.

Il y a tellement de choses  voir et  faire sur les Eco Markets. N'oubliez pas que la Native Nursery sera ouverte pendant le march de 8h00  midi pour tous vos besoins en plantes indignes.

Nikmati pasar terbuka ramah lingkungan di taman botani asli yang indah di IndigiScapes!

Habiskan pagi hari dengan berjalan-jalan di jalur pasar Botanic Gardens dan jelajahi berbagai kios unik, produk ramah lingkungan, dan produk segar yang tersedia dari komunitas pasar lokal dan kreatif.

Nikmati kopi, atau makan, di IndigiCafe; atau coba tarif fantastis dari van makanan.

Kunjungi penggeledahan koper populer untuk mendapatkan harga murah dan nikmati parade penggeledahan kami di atas panggung bersama Ranger Stacey.

Beristirahatlah sejenak di bawah rindangnya pepohonan, nikmati suasana santai dengan hiburan ramah keluarga dari The Little Wattlebird Band.

Anak-anak akan menyukai lukisan wajah flora dan fauna, permainan di luar ruangan, dan kerajinan alam di mana keluarga dapat mencoba menenun secara acak dan berkontribusi menenun teepee taman kami.

Ada begitu banyak hal yang bisa dilihat dan dilakukan di Eco Markets. Jangan lupa Native Nursery akan buka selama pasar mulai pukul 08.00 hingga tengah hari untuk semua kebutuhan tanaman asli Anda.

Genieen Sie umweltfreundliche Mrkte im Freien in der wunderschnen Umgebung des einheimischen botanischen Gartens von IndigiScapes!

Verbringen Sie den Morgen damit, durch die Marktgasse des Botanischen Gartens zu schlendern und die Auswahl an einzigartigen Stnden, nachhaltigen Produkten und frischen Erzeugnissen der lokalen und kreativen Marktgemeinschaft zu erkunden.

Gnnen Sie sich einen Kaffee oder eine Kleinigkeit zu essen im IndigiCafe oder probieren Sie die fantastischen Speisen von den Imbisswagen.

Besuchen Sie den beliebten Kofferstber, um ein gebrauchtes Schnppchen zu machen, und genieen Sie unsere Stberparade auf der Bhne mit Ranger Stacey.

Join them for a solid night of live entertainment at one of Australias best-quality comedy clubs. Showcasing some of Australia's best new talent, supported by celebrity headline acts.

Hand-selected quality lineups mean you're assured laughter from the get-go, then closed off with a professional headline act.

Previous headliners include; Steve Hughes, Dave O'Neil, Dave Hughes, Lehmo, Jimeoin, Luke Heggie, Denise Scott, Fiona O'Loughlin, Marty Sheargold, Richard Stubbs, Nick Cody and more!

Dpchez-vous et rservez maintenant. Allez-y... Vous mritez bien de rire !

Os programas de estreia de Kings of Comedy foram um grande sucesso, agora eles esto de volta para fazer tudo de novo! Desta vez com outra formao completamente diferente. Mantendo-o divertido e fresco. No perca esta vitrine incrvel.

Eles agora se mudaram para um novo local. Os mercados noturnos ao luar no Dreamworld!

Junte-se a eles para uma noite slida de entretenimento ao vivo em um dos clubes de comdia de melhor qualidade da Austrlia. Apresentando alguns dos melhores novos talentos da Austrlia, apoiados por celebridades.

Alinhamentos de qualidade selecionados a dedo significam que voc ter risadas garantidas desde o incio e, em seguida, encerrar com uma manchete profissional.

Os headliners anteriores incluem; Steve Hughes, Dave O'Neil, Dave Hughes, Lehmo, Jimeoin, Luke Heggie, Denise Scott, Fiona O'Loughlin, Marty Sheargold, Richard Stubbs, Nick Cody e muito mais!

Esta  realmente a noite que voc estava precisando. Freqentemente, os clientes saem da noite com dores no maxilar e no estmago, com uma vibrao positiva que no pode ser igualada.

Ento contrate uma bab, mande as crianas para os avs e desa para uma refeio deliciosa e uma noite inesquecvel. Ligue para aquela pessoa que voc estava querendo sair, agora voc tem uma 'boa desculpa'.

Faa deste aquele 'encontro noturno' especial que voc est precisando.

Apresse-se e reserve agora. V em frente... Voc merece uma boa risada!

Dois shows. Um adequado para famlias, todas as idades e o outro apenas para adultos.

Los estrenos de Kings of Comedy fueron un gran xito ahora han vuelto para hacerlo todo de nuevo! Esta vez con otra alineacin completamente diferente. Mantenindolo divertido y fresco. No te pierdas este increble escaparate.

Ahora se han mudado a una nueva ubicacin. Los mercados nocturnos a la luz de la luna en Dreamworld!

nase a ellos para disfrutar de una noche slida de entretenimiento en vivo en uno de los clubes de comedia de mejor calidad de Australia. Mostrando algunos de los mejores nuevos talentos de Australia, apoyados por celebridades.

Programaciones de calidad cuidadosamente seleccionadas significan que tienes asegurada la risa desde el principio, y luego cierran con un acto principal profesional.

Los cabezas de cartel anteriores incluyen; Steve Hughes, Dave O'Neil, Dave Hughes, Lehmo, Jimeoin, Luke Heggie, Denise Scott, Fiona O'Loughlin, Marty Sheargold, Richard Stubbs, Nick Cody y ms!

Esta es realmente la noche de fiesta que estabas necesitando. A menudo los clientes salen de la noche con la mandbula y el estmago doloridos y con una vibra positiva inigualable.

As que contrate una niera, enve a los nios con los abuelos y disfrute de una deliciosa comida y una noche que no olvidar. Llama a esa persona con la que has querido invitar a una cita, ahora tienes una "buena excusa".

Haz de esta esa "cita nocturna" especial que estabas necesitando.

Date prisa y reserva ahora. Adelante... Te mereces una buena risa!

Dos espectculos. Uno familiar para todas las edades y el otro solo para adultos.

Bergabunglah dengan mereka untuk menikmati hiburan live malam yang solid di salah satu klub komedi berkualitas terbaik di Australia. Menampilkan beberapa talenta baru terbaik Australia, didukung oleh artis-artis utama selebriti.

Jadi pesanlah pengasuh anak, kirim anak-anak ke Kakek-Nenek, dan pergilah ke sana untuk menikmati makanan lezat dan malam yang tidak akan Anda lupakan. Hubungi orang yang selama ini ingin Anda ajak kencan, sekarang Anda punya 'alasan bagus'.

Jadikan ini 'malam kencan' spesial yang Anda perlukan.

Buruan pesan sekarang. Ayo... Anda pantas tertawa!

Dua pertunjukan. Satu Ramah Keluarga Semua Usia dan satu lagi Khusus Dewasa.

I primi spettacoli di Kings of Comedy sono stati un enorme successo, ora sono tornati per rifarlo da capo! Questa volta con un'altra formazione completamente diversa. Mantenendolo divertente e fresco. Non perdetevi questa fantastica vetrina.

Ora si sono trasferiti in una nuova posizione. I mercati notturni al chiaro di luna a Dreamworld!

Unisciti a loro per una serata di intrattenimento dal vivo in uno dei comedy club pi rinomati d'Australia. In mostra alcuni dei migliori nuovi talenti australiani, supportati da spettacoli di celebrit.

Questa  davvero la serata fuori di cui avevi bisogno. Spesso i clienti lasciano la serata con la mascella e lo stomaco doloranti e con un'atmosfera positiva che non pu essere eguagliata.

Quindi prenota una babysitter, manda i bambini dai nonni e scendi per un pasto delizioso e una notte che non dimenticherai. Chiama la persona con cui volevi uscire, ora hai una "buona scusa".

Rendilo l'"appuntamento notturno" speciale di cui hai bisogno.

Affrettati e prenota subito. Vai avanti... Ti meriti una bella risata!

Due spettacoli. Uno adatto alle famiglie per tutte le et e l'altro solo per adulti.

_source.productDescription:
Join glass artisans Joanna Bone and Aaron Micallef for this unique glass sandblasting workshop. 

Youll learn the coldworking processes to stencil, mask and sandblast a permanent design onto a drinking glass that is yours to take home. 

Workshop includes expert tuition and all materials. Additional glasses may be purchased during the workshop.

Be quick - bookings are essential, places are limited!

You need to know:
This workshop is suitable for adults. People 12-17 years old may participate if accompanied by a ticket-holding adult.
No prior experience required.
Bookings are non-refundable and non-transferable.
Bring bottled water.
Participants must wear closed-in shoes for this workshop.

If you have any access or support requirements to participate fully in this event, please get in touch with the Museums friendly staff to discuss your options, 07 3432 5100.

_source.productName: Learn for Life - Caring for Your Family Treasures
_source.productDescription:
Join them for a presentation that will provide participants with practical methods for the long term care of their family history collections. This will include tips on safe storage, handling and display of paper, photographic, textile and three-dimensional objects.

Presented by professional conservator Lydia Egunnike. Lydia has a Masters of Applied Science in Cultural Conservation Studies and is a professional member of the Australian Institute for the Conservation of Cultural Material. She is an experienced paper and photographic conservator and has worked in the UK, the USA and Australia.

Before setting up her own conservation practice in 2020, she was a Museum Development Officer with the Queensland Museum Network and prior to that was Senior Conservator at the State Library of Queensland.

Registrations are essential. You must be an Ipswich Libraries member to register.

This event is presented by Ipswich Libraries as part of Galvanized  A Festival of Heritage.

_source.productName: Moreton Bay Farm Trail
_source.productDescription:
Join the Moreton Bay Farm Trail, a captivating celebration of the boutique local farms nestled within the picturesque Moreton Bay region. 

This ticketed event invites you to embark on a self-driving journey discovering local farms brimming with field-grown cut flowers, juicy strawberries, award-winning wine, sustainable meat products, fresh herbs and produce and more! 

With your ticket, you'll gain exclusive behind-the-scenes access to a diverse array of family-owned farms and farmers hubs. From backyard enterprises and small-scale plots to large commercial farms, youll be amazed at the diverse array of family-owned farms on Brisbanes doorstep.

When their gates swing open, you will experience a range of offerings - from flower picking, meandering through farm plots, listening to engaging farmer talks, to children's activities, there is something for everyone!

The Moreton Bay Farm Trail is a must-do experience for those who are passionate about supporting local farmers. It is a day not to be missed!

productComments.commentText:
Join the Moreton Bay Farm Trail, a captivating celebration of the boutique local farms nestled within the picturesque Moreton Bay region. 

This ticketed event invites you to embark on a self-driving journey discovering local farms brimming with field-grown cut flowers, juicy strawberries, award-winning wine, sustainable meat products, fresh herbs and produce and more! 

With your ticket, you'll gain exclusive behind-the-scenes access to a diverse array of family-owned farms and farmers hubs. From backyard enterprises and small-scale plots to large commercial farms, youll be amazed at the diverse array of family-owned farms on Brisbanes doorstep.

When their gates swing open, you will experience a range of offerings - from flower picking, meandering through farm plots, listening to engaging farmer talks, to children's activities, there is something for everyone!

The Moreton Bay Farm Trail is a must-do experience for those who are passionate about supporting local farmers. It is a day not to be missed!

nase a Moreton Bay Farm Trail, una cautivadora celebracin de las granjas locales boutique ubicadas en la pintoresca regin de Moreton Bay. 

Este evento con boleto lo invita a embarcarse en un viaje en automvil para descubrir granjas locales repletas de flores cortadas cultivadas en el campo, jugosas fresas, vino galardonado, productos crnicos sustentables, hierbas y productos frescos y ms. 

Con su boleto, obtendr acceso exclusivo detrs de escena a una variedad de granjas familiares y centros de agricultores. Desde empresas de traspatio y parcelas a pequea escala hasta grandes granjas comerciales, se sorprender con la variedad de granjas familiares a las puertas de Brisbane. 

Cuando sus puertas se abran, experimentar una variedad de ofertas: desde recolectar flores, pasear por las parcelas agrcolas, escuchar interesantes charlas de agricultores y actividades para nios hay algo para todos! 

Moreton Bay Farm Trail es una experiencia obligada para aquellos que sienten pasin por apoyar a los agricultores locales. Es un da que no te puedes perder!

Partecipa al Moreton Bay Farm Trail, un'affascinante celebrazione delle fattorie locali boutique immerse nella pittoresca regione di Moreton Bay. 

Questo evento a pagamento ti invita a intraprendere un viaggio in auto alla scoperta delle fattorie locali ricche di fiori recisi coltivati in campo, fragole succose, vino pluripremiato, prodotti a base di carne sostenibili, erbe fresche e prodotti agricoli e molto altro! 

Con il tuo biglietto, otterrai un accesso esclusivo dietro le quinte a una vasta gamma di fattorie a conduzione familiare e centri di agricoltori. Dalle aziende agricole e dai piccoli appezzamenti di terreno alle grandi fattorie commerciali, rimarrai stupito dalla vasta gamma di fattorie a conduzione familiare alle porte di Brisbane. 

Quando i loro cancelli si apriranno, sperimenterai una gamma di offerte: dalla raccolta dei fiori, alla passeggiata tra gli appezzamenti di terreno, all'ascolto di coinvolgenti discorsi degli agricoltori, alle attivit per bambini, ce n' per tutti i gusti! 

Il Moreton Bay Farm Trail  un'esperienza imperdibile per coloro che sono appassionati nel sostenere gli agricoltori locali.  una giornata da non perdere!

Participe da Moreton Bay Farm Trail, uma celebrao cativante das fazendas locais boutique aninhadas na pitoresca regio de Moreton Bay. 

Este evento com ingresso convida voc a embarcar em uma jornada autnoma descobrindo fazendas locais repletas de flores de corte cultivadas no campo, morangos suculentos, vinho premiado, produtos de carne sustentveis, ervas e produtos frescos e muito mais! 

Com seu ingresso, voc ter acesso exclusivo aos bastidores de uma variedade diversificada de fazendas familiares e centros de agricultores. De empresas de quintal e lotes de pequena escala a grandes fazendas comerciais, voc ficar surpreso com a variedade diversificada de fazendas familiares na porta de Brisbane.

Quando os portes se abrirem, voc experimentar uma variedade de ofertas - desde colher flores, passear por lotes agrcolas, ouvir conversas envolventes de agricultores at atividades infantis, h algo para todos!

A Moreton Bay Farm Trail  uma experincia imperdvel para aqueles que so apaixonados por apoiar os agricultores locais.  um dia imperdvel!

 -

Bergabunglah dengan Moreton Bay Farm Trail, perayaan menawan dari pertanian lokal butik yang terletak di wilayah Moreton Bay yang indah. 

Acara bertiket ini mengundang Anda untuk memulai perjalanan dengan berkendara sendiri menjelajahi pertanian lokal yang penuh dengan bunga potong yang ditanam di ladang, stroberi yang berair, anggur pemenang penghargaan, produk daging berkelanjutan, rempah segar dan hasil bumi, dan banyak lagi! 

Dengan tiket Anda, Anda akan memperoleh akses eksklusif di balik layar ke beragam pertanian milik keluarga dan pusat petani. Dari usaha pekarangan belakang dan lahan skala kecil hingga pertanian komersial besar, Anda akan kagum dengan beragamnya pertanian milik keluarga di depan pintu Brisbane.

Saat gerbang mereka terbuka, Anda akan merasakan berbagai penawaran - mulai dari memetik bunga, berkelok-kelok melalui lahan pertanian, mendengarkan pembicaraan petani yang menarik, hingga aktivitas anak-anak, ada sesuatu untuk semua orang!

Moreton Bay Farm Trail adalah pengalaman yang wajib dilakukan bagi mereka yang bersemangat mendukung petani lokal. Ini adalah hari yang tidak boleh dilewatkan!

Cet vnement payant vous invite  vous lancer dans un voyage en voiture  la dcouverte des fermes locales regorgeant de fleurs coupes cultives dans les champs, de fraises juteuses, de vins prims, de produits carns durables, d'herbes et de produits frais et bien plus encore! 

Avec votre billet, vous bnficierez d'un accs exclusif aux coulisses d'un large ventail de fermes familiales et de ples d'agriculteurs. Des entreprises artisanales et des parcelles  petite chelle aux grandes fermes commerciales, vous serez tonn par la diversit des fermes familiales aux portes de Brisbane. 

Lorsque leurs portes s'ouvriront, vous dcouvrirez une gamme d'offres - de la cueillette de fleurs, des promenades dans les parcelles agricoles, l'coute de discussions engageantes d'agriculteurs, aux activits pour enfants, il y en a pour tous les gots! 

Le Moreton Bay Farm Trail est une exprience incontournable pour ceux qui sont passionns par le soutien aux agriculteurs locaux. C'est une journe  ne pas manquer !

Nehmen Sie am Moreton Bay Farm Trail teil, einer fesselnden Feier der kleinen lokalen Bauernhfe in der malerischen Region Moreton Bay. 

Diese Ticketveranstaltung ldt Sie dazu ein, auf eigene Faust zu fahren und lokale Bauernhfe zu entdecken, die voller Schnittblumen aus Freilandanbau, saftiger Erdbeeren, preisgekrntem Wein, nachhaltiger Fleischprodukte, frischer Kruter und Produkte und vielem mehr sind! 

Mit Ihrem Ticket erhalten Sie exklusiven Zugang hinter die Kulissen einer vielfltigen Palette von familiengefhrten Bauernhfen und Farmerzentren. Von Hinterhofbetrieben und kleinen Parzellen bis hin zu groen kommerziellen Farmen werden Sie von der Vielfalt der familiengefhrten Bauernhfe vor Brisbanes Haustr begeistert sein.

Wenn sich ihre Tore ffnen, werden Sie eine Reihe von Angeboten erleben  vom Blumenpflcken, Schlendern durch die Farmparzellen, dem Anhren interessanter Farmergesprche bis hin zu Aktivitten fr Kinder ist fr jeden etwas dabei!

Der Moreton Bay Farm Trail ist ein Muss fr alle, die lokale Bauern leidenschaftlich untersttzen mchten. Diesen Tag sollten Sie sich nicht entgehen lassen!

_source.productName: Melbourne United v Cairns Taipans - NBL Blitz
_source.productDescription:
Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

productComments.commentText:
Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

Setelah Blitz terbesar dan terbaik dalam sejarah, NBL dengan bangga mengumumkan turnamen pramusimnya akan kembali ke Gold Coast pada bulan September.

Penggemar dari 10 tim akan melihat perubahan daftar nama untuk pertama kalinya, sementara pelatih dan pemain akan menyempurnakan rencana permainan mereka untuk musim ini.

Dunia bola basket datang ke Gold Coast tahun lalu dengan lebih dari 40 pencari bakat NBA dari 27 tim melihat sekilas empat NBL Next Stars yang dipilih dalam draft minggu lalu, termasuk pilihan nomor dua Alex Sarr.

Gold Coast akan kembali menjadi tuan rumah bagi industri bola basket internasional, karena Blitz tetap menjadi perjalanan pencarian bakat yang penting untuk menilai tim-tim baru NBL dan talenta-talenta Next Stars.

NBL telah bermitra dengan Experience Gold Coast dan Pemerintah Queensland untuk menghadirkan NBL Blitz ke Gold Coast.

Sulla scia del pi grande e migliore Blitz della storia, la NBL  orgogliosa di annunciare che il suo torneo pre-campionato torner sulla Gold Coast a settembre.

I tifosi di tutte e 10 le squadre potranno dare un primo sguardo ai roster rinnovati, mentre allenatori e giocatori metteranno a punto i loro piani di gioco per la campagna.

Il mondo del basket  arrivato alla Gold Coast lo scorso anno con pi di 40 scout NBA provenienti da 27 squadre che hanno dato il loro primo sguardo alle quattro NBL Next Stars selezionate nel draft della scorsa settimana, inclusa la scelta numero due Alex Sarr.

Explore Homer, Stony Creek's restored classic beer truck, sample a special Galvanized Ale, and enjoy exclusive festival meal deals and entertainment.  

Whats included:

History overview of the old Ipswich Pumpyard and our restored classic Brew Truck "Homer"
Brewery Tour
Tasting paddle of 4 beers with commentary by the brewer.
Warm Pretzel with butter
Can of our limited run Galvanized Brew
Goodie Bag including discount coupons for 20% off Draft and canned beer following the tour, meals following the tour and Stony Creek & 4Hearts merchandise.

Must be over 18 years - proof of identity required.

Families are welcome, including kids and fur-kids! Dont miss out, tickets are limited!

A Testament To The Legend Of 90s & 00s Club Culture.

Clubbing has always provided the antithesis to the normal, expected and mundane. A place to escape, connect and enter an alternate reality - tucked away safely in dimly lit, often secretive locations around the country. 

From Australias acid house infancy to the many reinventions of rave through the 90s and the peak of 00s nightlife, late-night communities were formed on the dancefloor. Lifelong friendships cemented over deep 4 am conversations, soundtracked by pure euphoria.

This unmatched era of nightlife has become a mythical moment in time, preserved only in patchy memories and faded photographs. 

Testament pays tribute to the sounds and the people of this club generation, and the vibrant late-night cities and cultures across the country which they cultivated.

Returning for another sell-out national tour, Ministry of Sound will be showcasing an iconic lineup of global legends, whose influence is woven into the fabric of modern club life. 

Celebrating the sweaty hedonistic 00s dancefloors at The Station on the Sunshine Coast; with Dutch heavyweight Laidback Luke (NL), big room house maestro Mousse T. (GER), and English electronic dance music duo X-Press 2 (UK) taking the helm.


Lineup: 
Laidback Luke 
Mousse T.
X-Press 2
Minx
Greg Sara
Mr Sparkles
Sgt Slick

A Testament To The Legend Of 90s & 00s Club Culture.

Clubbing has always provided the antithesis to the normal, expected and mundane. A place to escape, connect and enter an alternate reality - tucked away safely in dimly lit, often secretive locations around the country. 

From Australias acid house infancy to the many reinventions of rave through the 90s and the peak of 00s nightlife, late-night communities were formed on the dancefloor. Lifelong friendships cemented over deep 4 am conversations, soundtracked by pure euphoria.

This unmatched era of nightlife has become a mythical moment in time, preserved only in patchy memories and faded photographs. 

Testament pays tribute to the sounds and the people of this club generation, and the vibrant late-night cities and cultures across the country which they cultivated.

Returning for another sell-out national tour, Ministry of Sound will be showcasing an iconic lineup of global legends, whose influence is woven into the fabric of modern club life. 

Celebrating the sweaty hedonistic 00s dancefloors at The Station on the Sunshine Coast; with Dutch heavyweight Laidback Luke (NL), big room house maestro Mousse T. (GER), and English electronic dance music duo X-Press 2 (UK) taking the helm.

Um testamento  lenda da cultura dos clubes dos anos 90 e 2000.

As boates sempre forneceram a anttese do normal, esperado e mundano. Um lugar para escapar, conectar-se e entrar em uma realidade alternativa - escondido em segurana em locais pouco iluminados e muitas vezes secretos por todo o pas.

Desde a infncia do acid house na Austrlia at as muitas reinvenes da rave nos anos 90 e o auge da vida noturna dos anos 2000, comunidades noturnas foram formadas na pista de dana. Amizades para a vida toda cimentadas em conversas profundas s 4 da manh, com trilha sonora de pura euforia.

Esta era incomparvel da vida noturna tornou-se um momento mtico, preservado apenas em memrias irregulares e fotografias desbotadas.

Testament presta homenagem aos sons e s pessoas desta gerao club, e s vibrantes cidades e culturas noturnas em todo o pas que eles cultivaram.

Retornando para mais uma turn nacional com ingressos esgotados, o Ministry of Sound apresentar uma programao icnica de lendas globais, cuja influncia est presente na vida moderna dos clubes.

Comemorando as pistas de dana hedonistas e suadas dos anos 2000 no The Station on the Sunshine Coast; com o peso pesado holands Laidback Luke (NL), o maestro do big room House Mousse T. (ALE) e a dupla inglesa de msica eletrnica X-Press 2 (Reino Unido) assumindo o comando.


Alinhar:
Descontrado Lucas
Mousse T.
X-Pressione 2
Sirigaita
Greg Sara
Senhor Brilhante
Sargento esperto

Sebuah Bukti Legenda Budaya Klub 90an & 00an.

Clubbing selalu memberikan antitesis terhadap hal-hal normal, diharapkan, dan biasa-biasa saja. Tempat untuk melarikan diri, terhubung, dan memasuki realitas alternatif - tersembunyi dengan aman di lokasi yang remang-remang dan sering kali penuh rahasia di seluruh negeri.

Dari masa kanak-kanak acid house di Australia hingga penemuan kembali rave di tahun 90an dan puncak kehidupan malam tahun 00an, komunitas larut malam dibentuk di lantai dansa. Persahabatan seumur hidup terjalin melalui percakapan mendalam pada jam 4 pagi, diiringi oleh euforia murni.

Era kehidupan malam yang tak tertandingi ini telah menjadi momen mistis, hanya tersimpan dalam kenangan yang tidak lengkap dan foto-foto yang pudar.

Testament memberikan penghormatan kepada suara-suara dan orang-orang dari generasi klub ini, serta kota-kota dan budaya-budaya larut malam yang semarak di seluruh negara tempat mereka bekerja.

Kembali untuk tur nasional yang terjual habis, Ministry of Sound akan menampilkan jajaran legenda global yang ikonik, yang pengaruhnya terjalin dalam kehidupan klub modern.

Merayakan lantai dansa hedonistik tahun 00-an yang penuh keringat di The Station di Sunshine Coast; dengan kelas berat Belanda Laidback Luke (NL), maestro house house besar Mousse T. (GER), dan duo musik dansa elektronik Inggris X-Press 2 (Inggris) mengambil alih.

Un testimonio de la leyenda de la cultura de clubes de los aos 90 y 2000.

Las discotecas siempre han sido la anttesis de lo normal, lo esperado y lo mundano. Un lugar para escapar, conectarse y entrar en una realidad alternativa, escondido de forma segura en lugares poco iluminados y a menudo secretos de todo el pas.

Desde la infancia del acid house de Australia hasta las muchas reinvenciones del rave durante los aos 90 y el apogeo de la vida nocturna de los aos 2000, se formaron comunidades nocturnas en la pista de baile. Amistades de toda la vida cimentadas a travs de profundas conversaciones a las 4 am, acompaadas de pura euforia.

Esta era incomparable de la vida nocturna se ha convertido en un momento mtico, conservado slo en recuerdos irregulares y fotografas descoloridas.

Testament rinde homenaje a los sonidos y a la gente de esta generacin de clubes, y a las vibrantes ciudades y culturas nocturnas de todo el pas que cultivaron.

Al regresar para otra gira nacional con entradas agotadas, Ministry of Sound presentar una alineacin icnica de leyendas globales, cuya influencia est entretejida en la estructura de la vida moderna de los clubes.

Celebrando las sudorosas y hedonistas pistas de baile de los aos 2000 en The Station en Sunshine Coast; con el peso pesado holands Laidback Luke (NL), el maestro del big room house Mousse T. (GER) y el do ingls de msica electrnica de baile X-Press 2 (UK) tomando el mando.

Dall'infanzia dell'acid house australiana alle numerose reinvenzioni del rave negli anni '90 fino all'apice della vita notturna degli anni 2000, sulle piste da ballo si sono formate comunit notturne. Questa impareggiabile era di vita notturna  diventata un momento mitico, conservato solo in ricordi frammentari e fotografie sbiadite.

Testament rende omaggio ai suoni e alle persone di questa generazione di club, e alle vivaci citt e culture notturne di tutto il paese che hanno coltivato.

Di ritorno per un altro tour nazionale tutto esaurito, Ministry of Sound presenter una formazione iconica di leggende globali, la cui influenza  intessuta nel tessuto della vita dei club moderni.

Clubbing war schon immer das Gegenteil von dem Normalen, Erwarteten und Alltglichen. Ein Ort, um zu entkommen, Kontakte zu knpfen und in eine andere Realitt einzutauchen  sicher versteckt an schwach beleuchteten, oft geheimen Orten im ganzen Land.

Von den Anfngen des australischen Acid House bis zu den vielen Neuerfindungen des Raves in den 90ern und dem Hhepunkt des Nachtlebens in den 00ern bildeten sich auf der Tanzflche Late-Night-Communitys. Lebenslange Freundschaften wurden bei tiefgrndigen Gesprchen um 4 Uhr morgens gefestigt, untermalt von purer Euphorie.

_source.productDescription:
Immerse yourself in an unforgettable experience filled with live entertainment, delectable Serbian food and sweets, exciting kids rides, captivating Serbian dancing, and competitions with fantastic prizes to be won!

This incredible event is proudly brought to you by the Serbian Orthodox Church Woolloongabba, who have worked tirelessly to create a festival that showcases the rich heritage of Serbia right here in Brisbane.

For more information, be sure to visit their social media pages. Stay updated on all the festival happenings and join the conversation with fellow attendees. It's going to be a day filled with cultural delights, and cherished memories for all!

Don't miss out on this opportunity to experience the vibrant spirit of Serbia in the heart of Brisbane. Spread the word, invite your friends and family, and get ready for an amazing day at Vaar!

_source.productDescription:
After exploding into the world's view at the tail end of 2023, Western Australia's own SRB are coming home from a sold-out debut European tour with a new album and a new Aussie tour. 'D.I.Y' - a mantra that SRB knows all too well, and also ironically the name of the first album not released by the, after signing a global record deal with Cooking Vinyl Australia earlier this year. 

'D.I.Y' is out everywhere and tickets for the tour are on sale now!

This is an 18-plus event.
