productComments.commentText:
After exploding into the world's view at the tail end of 2023, Western Australia's own SRB are coming home from a sold-out debut European tour with a new album and a new Aussie tour. 'D.I.Y' - a mantra that SRB knows all too well, and also ironically the name of the first album not released by the, after signing a global record deal with Cooking Vinyl Australia earlier this year. 

'D.I.Y' is out everywhere and tickets for the tour are on sale now!

This is an 18-plus event.

Despus de explotar a la vista del mundo a finales de 2023, la propia SRB de Australia Occidental regresa a casa de una gira europea debut con entradas agotadas con un nuevo lbum y una nueva gira por Australia. 'D.I.Y': un mantra que SRB conoce muy bien y, irnicamente, tambin es el nombre del primer lbum que no lanz, despus de firmar un contrato discogrfico global con Cooking Vinyl Australia a principios de este ao. 

'D.I.Y' est disponible en todas partes y las entradas para la gira ya estn a la venta!

Este es un evento para mayores de 18 aos.

Dopo essere esplosi alla ribalta mondiale alla fine del 2023, gli SRB dell'Australia Occidentale tornano a casa da un tour europeo di debutto tutto esaurito con un nuovo album e un nuovo tour australiano. 'D.I.Y' - un mantra che SRB conosce fin troppo bene, e ironicamente anche il nome del primo album non pubblicato dalla SRB, dopo aver firmato un contratto discografico globale con Cooking Vinyl Australia all'inizio di quest'anno. 

'D.I.Y'  uscito ovunque e i biglietti per il tour sono in vendita ora!

_source.productName: Creedence - 10th Anniversary Tour  - Beenleigh Tavern - Beenleigh
_source.productDescription:
Join them in celebrating a decade of timeless rock 'n' roll with Creedence: The John Fogerty Shows 10th Anniversary Tour!

For the past ten years, we've been bringing the electrifying spirit of Creedence Clearwater Revival and John Fogerty to stages all around the world, and now it's time to mark this incredible journey with a tour like no other.

Get ready to be transported back to the heyday of American rock as they pay homage to one of the greatest bands in music history. From the swampy blues-rock of "Green River" to the anthemic "Bad Moon Rising" and the heart-wrenching balladry of "Have You Ever Seen the Rain" we faithfully recreate all the hits that made Creedence Clearwater Revival legendary.

The 10th Anniversary Tour promises a night of nostalgia, high-energy performance, and an unforgettable experience for die-hard fans and new listeners alike. With our captivating frontman, Andre Lemberg, channelling John Fogertyand an All-Star band of musicians who regularly play with Angry Anderson, Mark Gable of the Choirboys and have shared stages with Uriah Heep, Jimmy Barnes and The Angels, we bring the spirit of CCR and Fogerty to life.

Grab your tickets now, and let's keep the rock 'n' roll revival rolling!

productComments.commentText:
Every year Chinchilla transforms into a vibrant sensory feast, celebrating the multicultural community with top-notch international cuisine and entertainment.

The main street is transformed into one big alfresco dining area and street party with a single long table running in the middle. Food stalls offer dishes from various international cuisines, as visitors enjoy live dance and music performances and kids activities. This free event has been organised since 2010, highly anticipated and a highlight for the region.

Don't miss out on being a part of this vibrant event that brings people together and experience Chinchilla's hospitality!

Todos os anos, o Chinchilla se transforma em um vibrante banquete sensorial, celebrando a comunidade multicultural com culinria e entretenimento internacional de alto nvel.

A rua principal  transformada em uma grande rea de jantar ao ar livre e festa de rua com uma nica mesa comprida no meio. As barracas de comida oferecem pratos de diversas cozinhas internacionais, enquanto os visitantes desfrutam de apresentaes de dana e msica ao vivo e atividades infantis. Este evento gratuito  organizado desde 2010, muito aguardado e um destaque para a regio.

No perca a oportunidade de fazer parte deste evento vibrante que rene as pessoas e vivencia a hospitalidade da Chinchila!

Chaque anne, Chinchilla se transforme en un festin sensoriel vibrant, clbrant la communaut multiculturelle avec une cuisine et des divertissements internationaux de premier ordre.

La rue principale est transforme en une grande salle  manger en plein air et une fte de rue avec une seule longue table au milieu. Les stands de nourriture proposent des plats de diverses cuisines internationales, tandis que les visiteurs profitent de spectacles de danse et de musique en direct et d'activits pour les enfants. Cet vnement gratuit est organis depuis 2010, trs attendu et constitue un moment fort pour la rgion.

Ne manquez pas de participer  cet vnement dynamique qui rassemble les gens et dcouvrez l'hospitalit de Chinchilla!

Setiap tahun Chinchilla berubah menjadi pesta sensorik yang semarak, merayakan komunitas multikultural dengan masakan dan hiburan internasional terbaik.

Jalan utama diubah menjadi ruang makan alfresco besar dan pesta jalanan dengan satu meja panjang di tengahnya. Kedai makanan menawarkan hidangan dari berbagai masakan internasional, saat pengunjung menikmati pertunjukan tari dan musik live serta aktivitas anak-anak. Acara gratis ini telah diselenggarakan sejak tahun 2010, sangat dinantikan dan menjadi sorotan di wilayah ini.

Jangan lewatkan untuk menjadi bagian dari acara penuh semangat yang menyatukan orang-orang dan merasakan keramahtamahan Chinchilla!

Jedes Jahr verwandelt sich Chinchilla in ein pulsierendes Fest der Sinne, bei dem die multikulturelle Gemeinschaft mit erstklassiger internationaler Kche und Unterhaltung gefeiert wird.

Die Hauptstrae verwandelt sich in einen groen Essbereich im Freien und ein Straenfest mit einem einzigen langen Tisch in der Mitte. Essensstnde bieten Gerichte aus verschiedenen internationalen Kchen an, whrend die Besucher Live-Tanz- und Musikdarbietungen und Aktivitten fr Kinder genieen. Diese kostenlose Veranstaltung wird seit 2010 organisiert, ist mit Spannung erwartet und ein Highlight fr die Region.

Verpassen Sie nicht, Teil dieser pulsierenden Veranstaltung zu sein, die Menschen zusammenbringt und Chinchillas Gastfreundschaft erlebt!

Cada ao, Chinchilla se transforma en un vibrante festn sensorial que celebra la comunidad multicultural con entretenimiento y cocina internacional de primer nivel.

La calle principal se transforma en un gran comedor al aire libre y fiesta callejera con una nica mesa larga en el medio. Los puestos de comida ofrecen platos de diversas cocinas internacionales, mientras los visitantes disfrutan de espectculos de danza y msica en vivo y actividades para nios. Este evento gratuito se organiza desde 2010, es muy esperado y un momento destacado para la regin.

No te pierdas ser parte de este vibrante evento que rene a las personas y experimenta la hospitalidad de Chinchilla!

_source.productDescription:
Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

Off the back of the biggest and best Blitz in history, the NBL is proud to announce its pre-season tournament will return to the Gold Coast in September.

Fans from all 10 teams will get their first look at the revamped rosters, while coaches and players will fine-tune their gameplans for the campaign.

The basketball world came to the Gold Coast last year with more than 40 NBA scouts from 27 teams getting their first glimpse at the four NBL Next Stars selected in last weeks draft, including number two pick Alex Sarr.

The Gold Coast will again host the interest of the international basketball industry, as the Blitz remains a crucial scouting trip to assess the new crop of NBL teams and Next Stars talent.

The NBL has partnered with Experience Gold Coastand the Queensland Goverment to bring the NBL Blitz to the Gold Coast.

Setelah Blitz terbesar dan terbaik dalam sejarah, NBL dengan bangga mengumumkan turnamen pramusimnya akan kembali diadakan di Gold Coast pada bulan September.

Penggemar dari 10 tim akan melihat perubahan daftar nama untuk pertama kalinya, sementara pelatih dan pemain akan menyempurnakan rencana permainan mereka untuk musim ini.

Dunia bola basket datang ke Gold Coast tahun lalu dengan lebih dari 40 pencari bakat NBA dari 27 tim melihat sekilas empat NBL Next Stars yang dipilih dalam draft minggu lalu, termasuk pilihan nomor dua Alex Sarr.

Gold Coast akan kembali menjadi tuan rumah bagi industri bola basket internasional, karena Blitz tetap menjadi perjalanan pencarian bakat yang penting untuk menilai tim-tim baru NBL dan talenta-talenta Next Stars.

NBL telah bermitra dengan Experience Gold Coast dan Pemerintah Queensland untuk menghadirkan NBL Blitz ke Gold Coast.

Nach dem grten und besten Blitz aller Zeiten ist die NBL stolz, bekannt geben zu knnen, dass ihr Vorsaisonturnier im September an die Gold Coast zurckkehrt.

Fans aller 10 Teams erhalten einen ersten Blick auf die berarbeiteten Kader, whrend Trainer und Spieler ihre Spielplne fr die Saison verfeinern.

Die Basketballwelt kam letztes Jahr an die Gold Coast, als mehr als 40 NBA-Scouts von 27 Teams einen ersten Blick auf die vier NBL Next Stars erhaschen konnten, die letzte Woche im Draft ausgewhlt wurden, darunter auch Nummer zwei Alex Sarr.

Die Gold Coast wird erneut das Interesse der internationalen Basketballbranche wecken, da der Blitz weiterhin ein wichtiger Scouting-Trip bleibt, um die neuen NBL-Teams und Next Stars-Talente zu bewerten.

Die NBL hat sich mit Experience Gold Coast und der Regierung von Queensland zusammengetan, um den NBL Blitz an die Gold Coast zu bringen.

Aps a maior e melhor Blitz da histria, a NBL tem o orgulho de anunciar que seu torneio de pr-temporada retornar  Gold Coast em setembro.

Os torcedores de todos os 10 times vero pela primeira vez as escalaes renovadas, enquanto os treinadores e jogadores ajustaro seus planos de jogo para a campanha.

O mundo do basquete chegou  Gold Coast no ano passado com mais de 40 olheiros da NBA de 27 times tendo sua primeira viso dos quatro NBL Next Stars selecionados no draft da semana passada, incluindo o nmero dois, Alex Sarr.

A Gold Coast ser novamente a sede do interesse da indstria internacional do basquete, j que o Blitz continua sendo uma viagem de reconhecimento crucial para avaliar a nova safra de times da NBL e talentos do Next Stars.

A NBL fez parceria com a Experience Gold Coast e o governo de Queensland para trazer o NBL Blitz para a Gold Coast.

_source.productName: Brisbane Arcade Spring Show 2024 - 100th Birthday Edition
_source.productDescription:
Celebrating a centenary of style, Brisbane Arcades annual night of nights  Brisbane Arcade Spring Show 2024 - 100th Birthday Edition  will be staged on Saturday, 7th September.

Brisbane Arcades Spring Show is a premium seated evening fashion parade under the stars on the Queen Street Mall featuring spring/summer collections from Brisbane Arcades esteemed fashion, jewellery and accessory designers and boutiques.

Issada Cosmeceuticals will be presenting the make-up for our runway models.

The runway show will be followed by a decadent cocktail party inside the grand and exquisite Brisbane Arcade with a magnificent and substantial cocktail menu matched with sparkling and still wines, beers and soft drinks.

This much-loved event is one of the most exclusive and memorable occasions on Brisbanes fashion and social calendars.

Ticket price includes bubbles on arrival, premium seating at the runway show followed by cocktail-after-party until 10pm including beverages and canapes.

The fashion runway show will be held in Queen Street Mall  adjacent to Brisbane Arcade -and seating for the show will commence at 7pm sharp.

Tickets available online.

Celebrating a centenary of style, Brisbane Arcades annual night of nights  Brisbane Arcade Spring Show 2024 - 100th Birthday Edition  will be staged on Saturday, 7th September.

Brisbane Arcades Spring Show is a premium seated evening fashion parade under the stars on the Queen Street Mall featuring spring/summer collections from Brisbane Arcades esteemed fashion, jewellery and accessory designers and boutiques.

Issada Cosmeceuticals will be presenting the make-up for our runway models.

The runway show will be followed by a decadent cocktail party inside the grand and exquisite Brisbane Arcade with a magnificent and substantial cocktail menu matched with sparkling and still wines, beers and soft drinks.

This much-loved event is one of the most exclusive and memorable occasions on Brisbanes fashion and social calendars.

Ticket price includes bubbles on arrival, premium seating at the runway show followed by cocktail-after-party until 10pm including beverages and canapes.

The fashion runway show will be held in Queen Street Mall  adjacent to Brisbane Arcade -and seating for the show will commence at 7pm sharp.

Tickets available online.

_source.productDescription:
Get ready to turn up at The Station, Birtinya  on Saturday, 7th September! Like A Boss brings you the hardest hitters in Aussie hip hop and rap, backed by a killer DJ lineup that'll keep the vibes high from 2 PM to 10PM!

Headliners Hooligan Hefs  Bringing the heat with his hard-hitting anthems!

The 046, Lisi,  Say True God, Big Noyz, DC, Jaecy, Lil Mase, Yxan X TMK.
 
DJ Line-up: Ramos, Atlaz, MAARV, Wreckah, Ellen Rose

This isn't just a festivalit's a movement. A full day of the freshest beats, the rawest rhymes, and the dopest vibes. You don't want to miss out on this epic celebration of hip hop culture!

Known for hosting some of the coasts best live music, with its laid-back vibe, epic sound, and welcoming atmosphere, its the perfect spot to enjoy the fest up close and personal. Whether youre a local or just passing through, dont miss the chance to see this incredible lineup light up the stage . Get ready for a night of unforgettable music at The Station!

With accessibility considered, The Station welcomes all abilities and strives to create a welcoming and fun experience for everyone. Check out companion website Crge to learn more about the venue and the tools to help make your visit a breeze

This is a 16+ event

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Offer multiple options for booking - web, email, phone
Offer a range of contact methods for receiving complaints
Train your staff in disability awareness
Have accessibility information and photos, including of a bathroom, room and/or floor plan on your website (can be emailed on request)
Ask all visitors if there are any specific needs to be met
Provide assistance with booking arrangements (includes providing clear  itineraries with written instructions  on what to do at various destinations)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Welcomes and assists people who have challenges with learning, communication, understanding and behaviour. (includes people with autism, intellectual disability, Down syndrome, acquired brain injury (ABI), dyslexia and dementia)

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Use Plain English / easy read signage and information (includes menus and emergency information)
A quiet space is available at the venue/ facility

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people who are blind or have vision loss.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Have  Braille and tactile signage on all information and paths of travel
Provide digital communication materials (hard copy information is also available on line)
Use easy read fonts in your signage and communication materials (Helvetica and Arial)
Have an appropriate area for toileting an assistance dog
Have handrails on all your stairways
Have Exit signs which are visible at a ground level (high level signs are difficult to see in a fire)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people with sufficient mobility to climb a few steps but who would benefit from fixtures to aid balance. (This includes people using walking frames and mobility aids)

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Use floors/coverings which are slip resistant, firm and smooth
Use non-slip tiles in the bathroom or slip resistant matting
Have grab rails in the bathroom
Provide seating in common areas including reception area

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people who use a wheelchair.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Have step free outdoor pathways (includes picnic areas, barbecues and shelters)
Have a step free main entrance to the building and/or reception area (includes ramps or slopes with a maximum gradient of 1:14, otherwise are too steep for wheelchairs)
Have step free access to restaurant, lounge and bar
Have step free access to the conference or function room
Have accessible seating areas in theatrette
Have doorways which are easy to open and have lever handles (doorways 850mm or wider when open and not heavy)
Have an accessible public toilet which is unlocked
Have a wheelchair accessible toilet / shower and change room
Have wheelchair accessible picnic tables (picnic tables require 720mm knee clearance and 800mm maximum height)
Have a wheelchair/scooter charging station (power point) in an accessible location
Have at least one wheelchair accessible parking space with wheelchair accessible signage clearly displayed (International standards are 3200mm wide x 2500 mm high)

Have wheelchair accessible transport options available in the general vicinity (provide information on name of the operator, phone and website link to individual providers for private vehicles, community transport train, mini vans, hire cars, buses, taxis, ferry, tram, light rail etc in your access statement)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people with allergies and intolerances.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Modify your cooking and cleaning practices to cater for people with food allergies or chemical intolerances (could include menus with meals free from: nuts, dairy, seafood, eggs, gluten etc)
Train your staff to respond to allergic reactions
Adhere to The Food Authority requirements for allergy management in food preparation
Have equipment to respond to anaphylactic shock such as epipens and defibrillator

Bersiaplah untuk tampil di The Station, Birtinya pada hari Sabtu, 7 September! Like A Boss menghadirkan para musisi hip hop dan rap Australia yang paling hebat, didukung oleh jajaran DJ yang akan membuat suasana tetap meriah dari pukul 14.00 hingga 22.00!

Penampil utama Hooligan Hefs  Membawakan lagu-lagu hit-nya yang hebat!

The 046, Lisi, Say True God, Big Noyz, DC, Jaecy, Lil Mase, Yxan X TMK.

Jajaran DJ: Ramos, Atlaz, MAARV, Wreckah, Ellen Rose

Ini bukan sekadar festivalini adalah sebuah gerakan. Sehari penuh dengan ketukan paling segar, rima paling mentah, dan suasana paling keren. Anda tidak ingin melewatkan perayaan budaya hip hop yang epik ini!

Terkenal karena menjadi tuan rumah bagi beberapa musik live terbaik di pesisir, dengan suasana santai, suara epik, dan atmosfer yang ramah, tempat ini adalah tempat yang sempurna untuk menikmati festival dari dekat dan personal.
